UI Module¶

The UI module contains the files automatically generated by the Qt UI compiler. These files define the structure and graphical user interface (GUI) elements for various application components. Using PySide6, they allow you to create, configure and manage the different dialogs and windows of the application, thus facilitating a consistent and functional user experience.
